node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by @freshhkiicks on August 10, 2021 tagging @aleimages. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
Just here to remind y’all to keep pushing! 
At one point in my life I was spending my last $20 just to put gas in my tank & barley made it to work. Never hits me but now I have my dream car & gas is my least worry. When you feel like all odds are against you & everything is negative it’s because you have a positive future ahead 💪🏽
Last day to get Merch! Next drop won’t be til Black Friday‼️LINK IN BIO 🔥

node.text:
Leggo 🔥 Limited merch dropping tomorrow 3pm PST Birthday drop 🎁
If you want to get me a gift tmw just buy some Merch 😂
I will be picking 3 people for $100 credit for the store‼️ All you have to do is make a post of your car with hashtag #fbotunebroo 
I will pick my top 3 favorite builds by 10pm pst tonight & repost on my story!  Excited for the drop let’s sell out a 3rd time 🔥

Let’s gooo 🔥 Another limited drop coming this Thursday on my birthday August 5th 🎁

Link In bio to subscribe for email notification when it drops Thursday!
